<p>
Configuration files:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="buffindexed.conf.html">buffindexed.conf</a> &mdash; Configuration for the buffindexed overview method (<a href="samples/buffindexed.conf">example</a>)</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="control.ctl.html">control.ctl</a> &mdash; Specify handling of Usenet control messages (<a href="samples/control.ctl">example</a>)</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="cycbuff.conf.html">cycbuff.conf</a> &mdash; Configuration for the CNFS storage backend (<a href="samples/cycbuff.conf">example</a>)</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="distrib.pats.html">distrib.pats</a> &mdash; Default values for the Distribution: header (<a href="samples/distrib.pats">example</a>)</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="distributions.html">distributions</a> &mdash; Recommended values for the Distribution: header (<a href="samples/distributions">example</a>)</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="expire.ctl.html">expire.ctl</a> &mdash; Configuration file for article expiration (<a href="samples/expire.ctl">example</a>)</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="incoming.conf.html">incoming.conf</a> &mdash; Configuration of incoming news feeds (<a href="samples/incoming.conf">example</a>)</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="inn-radius.conf.html">inn-radius.conf</a> &mdash; Configuration for nnrpd RADIUS authenticator (<a href="samples/inn-radius.conf">example</a>)</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="inn.conf.html">inn.conf</a> &mdash; Basic configuration data for INN programs (<a href="samples/inn.conf">example</a>)</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="innfeed.conf.html">innfeed.conf</a> &mdash; Configuration file for innfeed (<a href="samples/innfeed.conf">example</a>)</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="moderators.html">moderators</a> &mdash; Submission addresses for moderated groups (<a href="samples/moderators">example</a>)</li>

<li class="packed"><a href="motd.news.html">motd.news</a> &mdash; Message of the day information for feeders or readers
    (sample <a href="samples/motd.innd">motd.innd</a>,
     <a href="samples/motd.nnrpd">motd.nnrpd</a>)</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="newsfeeds.html">newsfeeds</a> &mdash; Determine where Usenet articles are sent (<a href="samples/newsfeeds">example</a>)</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="nntpsend.ctl.html">nntpsend.ctl</a> &mdash; List of sites to feed via nntpsend (<a href="samples/nntpsend.ctl">example</a>)</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="passwd.nntp.html">passwd.nntp</a> &mdash; Passwords for connecting to remote NNTP servers (<a href="samples/passwd.nntp">example</a>)</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="readers.conf.html">readers.conf</a> &mdash; Access control and configuration for nnrpd (<a href="samples/readers.conf">example</a>)</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="storage.conf.html">storage.conf</a> &mdash; Configuration file for storage manager (<a href="samples/storage.conf">example</a>)</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="subscriptions.html">subscriptions</a> &mdash; Default recommended subscribed groups (<a href="samples/subscriptions">example</a>)</li>
</ul>

<p>
Primary daemons and utilities to start them:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="ctlinnd.html">ctlinnd</a> &mdash; Control the main INN daemon</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="innd.html">innd</a> &mdash; Core daemon for accepting and storing articles</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="nnrpd.html">nnrpd</a> &mdash; NNTP reader server</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="rc.news.html">rc.news</a> &mdash; Start or stop INN daemons</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="tinyleaf.html">tinyleaf</a> &mdash; Very simple IHAVE-only NNTP server</li>
</ul>

<p>
Data files:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="active.html">active</a> &mdash; List of newsgroups carried by the server (<a href="samples/active">example</a>)</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="active.times.html">active.times</a> &mdash; List of local creation times of newsgroups</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="newsgroups.html">newsgroups</a> &mdash; List of newsgroups and their short descriptions (<a href="samples/newsgroups">example</a>)</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="newslog.html">newslog</a> &mdash; Description of INN log files</li>
</ul>

<p>
Outgoing feeds:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="batcher.html">batcher</a> &mdash; Prepare UUCP batches</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="buffchan.html">buffchan</a> &mdash; Buffered backend for generating batch files</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="innfeed.html">innfeed, imapfeed</a> &mdash; Multi-host, multi-connection, streaming NNTP feeder</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="innxmit.html">innxmit</a> &mdash; Send Usenet articles to a remote NNTP server</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="nntpsend.html">nntpsend</a> &mdash; Send Usenet articles to remote sites</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="send-uucp.html">send-uucp</a> &mdash; Send Usenet articles via UUCP</li>
</ul>

<p>
Article posting utilities:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="inews.html">inews</a> &mdash; Post an article to the local news server</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="mailpost.html">mailpost</a> &mdash; Feed an e-mail message into a newsgroup</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="pullnews.html">pullnews</a> &mdash; Pull news from news servers and feed it to another</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="rnews.html">rnews</a> &mdash; Inject individual articles and UUCP batches</li>
</ul>

<p>
Overview method documentation:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="ovdb.html">OVDB</a></li>
</ul>

